2. Then sum up their amounts to get the total financial expenses

- 2024-01-06: Financial Expenses of 8,372.35
- 2024-01-11: Financial Expenses of 16,035.97
- 2024-02-04: Financial Expenses of 19,717.55
- 2024-02-05: Financial Expenses of 18,330.82

Summing up these values:
4,678.66 + 8,372.35 + 16,035.97 + 19,717.55 + 18,330.82 = 67,135.35
